%% JWT Authentication Flow

sequenceDiagram
    actor U as 👤 用户
    participant C as 🖥 CLI / SDK
    participant A as 🚀 FastAPI
    participant H as 🔐 bcrypt
    participant J as 🎫 JWT

    Note over U,J: ── 注册 ──
    U->>C: register(username, email, password)
    C->>A: POST /api/auth/register
    A->>H: hash_password(password)
    H-->>A: $2b$...hashed
    A->>A: INSERT INTO users
    A->>J: create_access_token(sub=user.id)
    J-->>A: eyJhbG...token
    A-->>C: {access_token, user}
    C->>C: save to ~/.mlp/config.json

    Note over U,J: ── 登录 ──
    U->>C: login(email, password)
    C->>A: POST /api/auth/login
    A->>A: SELECT user WHERE email=?
    A->>H: verify_password(password, hash)
    H-->>A: ✓ match
    A->>J: create_access_token(...)
    J-->>A: eyJhbG...token
    A-->>C: {access_token}

    Note over U,J: ── API 请求 (已认证) ──
    U->>C: experiments create
    C->>A: GET /api/experiments + Bearer token
    A->>J: decode + verify(token)
    J-->>A: {sub: user_id}
    A->>A: get_current_user → User ORM
    A-->>C: response
